OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother mostly dry day with
OL,6,Fsome hot or very hot spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine around. Rather more cloud and
OL,8,Fa little cooler across Argyll where
OL,9,Fthe odd afternoon shower is possible.
OL,10,FMainly light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Outbreaks of heavy
OL,14,Fthundery rain, risk of hail, through
OL,15,Fthe early hours. Drier later across
OL,16,FArgyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,179,160,301,260,100,100
PN,17802
